summary: 该插件用于检测Nexus Repository Manager中的多个漏洞，包括CVE-2019-7238、CVE-2020-10199、CVE-2020-10204、CVE-2020-24571以及默认弱口令和目录遍历问题。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect multiple vulnerabilities in Nexus Repository Manager, including CVE-2019-7238, CVE-2020-10199, CVE-2020-10204, CVE-2020-24571, default weak passwords, and directory traversal issues.
